    "title": "Reckitt India Holdings Services is Hiring: Quality Control Engineer (Senior)",
    "description": "We at Reckitt India Holdings Services are looking for an experienced Quality Control Engineer based out of Delhi. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Reckitt India Holdings Services:\nReckitt India Holdings Services is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in TPM\n• Proficiency in Root Cause Analysis\n• Proficiency in PLC/SCADA\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Delhi, Delhi, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Reckitt India Holdings Services!",
